---
import { DollarSign, Gauge, Smartphone, TriangleAlert } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section class="w-full px-4 sm:px-8 py-16 lg:py-24 bg-bgMain brutal-border-b relative z-10">
	<div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto observe-block">
		<div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-between items-start lg:items-end mb-16 gap-10">
			<div>
				<span class="text-[12px] font-mono font-bold text-primary uppercase tracking-widest block mb-4">[ 01. The Problem ]</span>
				<h2 class="text-fluid-h2 leading-[0.95] font-bold uppercase flex flex-col">
					<span class="reveal-overflow"><span class="reveal-text block">Is Your Site</span></span>
					<span class="reveal-overflow"><span class="reveal-text block text-outline inline-block transform -rotate-2 origin-left">A Liability?</span></span>
				</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="stamp-item delay-200 bg-warning border-[4px] border-black p-5 shadow-[8px_8px_0_0_#000] max-w-md transform rotate-1">
				<span class="text-[12px] font-bold font-mono block mb-2 bg-black text-warning inline-block px-2 py-0.5 border border-black">[ SYSTEM WARNING ]</span>
				<p class="text-[16px] md:text-[18px] font-[600] text-black leading-tight">
					Most local business websites are slow, outdated, or barely maintained. They quietly lose visitors, leads, and trust every day.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 lg:gap-8 mb-12">
			<div class="stamp-item relative shadow-[8px_8px_0_0_#000] delay-100 bg-white border-4 border-black p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
				<div class="absolute -top-3 -right-3 bg-[#EF4444] text-white font-bold font-mono text-[12px] px-2 py-1 border-2 border-black transform rotate-6 shadow-[2px_2px_0_0_#000] z-10">[ 404 UX ]</div>
				<Gauge className="w-10 h-10 lg:w-12 lg:h-12 mb-6 text-black" strokeWidth={2.5} />
				<h3 class="text-[20px] lg:text-[22px] font-black uppercase mb-3">Slow &<br>Bloated</h3>
				<p class="text-[15px] text-textSecondary font-[600] leading-snug">Taking 5+ seconds to load kills your Google ranking and frustrates users.</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="stamp-item relative shadow-[8px_8px_0_0_#000] delay-200 bg-white border-4 border-black p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
				<div class="absolute -top-3 -left-3 bg-primary text-white font-bold font-mono text-[12px] px-2 py-1 border-2 border-black transform -rotate-3 shadow-[2px_2px_0_0_#000] z-10">[ FATAL ]</div>
				<Smartphone className="w-10 h-10 lg:w-12 lg:h-12 mb-6 text-black" strokeWidth={2.5} />
				<h3 class="text-[20px] lg:text-[22px] font-black uppercase mb-3">Mobile<br>Broken</h3>
				<p class="text-[15px] text-textSecondary font-[600] leading-snug">A broken mobile experience guarantees lost local searches to competitors.</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="stamp-item relative shadow-[8px_8px_0_0_#000] delay-300 bg-warning text-black border-4 border-black p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
				<div class="absolute -top-4 right-4 bg-black text-warning font-bold font-mono text-[12px] px-2 py-1 border-2 border-warning transform rotate-2 shadow-[4px_4px_0_0_#000] z-10">[ HAZARD ]</div>
				<TriangleAlert className="w-10 h-10 lg:w-12 lg:h-12 mb-6 text-black" strokeWidth={2.5} />
				<h3 class="text-[20px] lg:text-[22px] font-black uppercase mb-3">Abandoned<br>Code</h3>
				<p class="text-[15px] font-[600] leading-snug">Built on old plugins by a developer who vanished. Massive security risk.</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="stamp-item relative shadow-[8px_8px_0_0_#000] delay-400 bg-black text-white border-4 border-black p-6 lg:p-8 flex flex-col hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
				<div class="absolute top-1/2 -right-4 bg-[#EF4444] text-white font-bold font-mono text-[12px] px-2 py-1 border-2 border-black transform -translate-y-1/2 rotate-90 shadow-[2px_2px_0_0_#000] z-10">$$$ LOST</div>
				<DollarSign className="w-10 h-10 lg:w-12 lg:h-12 mb-6 text-white" strokeWidth={2.5} />
				<h3 class="text-[20px] lg:text-[22px] font-black uppercase mb-3">Lost<br>Leads</h3>
				<p class="text-[15px] text-gray-300 font-[600] leading-snug">Forms silently fail, calls aren't tracked, and opportunities slip away.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
